    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use to describe a surface that has been carved, molded, or stamped so that an image or design projects from or is sunk into a continuous surface.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
